list.item:
Embassies of action addressee capitals will be receiving by pouch the
                        following documents: 

—a joint U.S.–U.K. letter from Secretaries Kissinger and Crosland on the Zimbabwe
                                Development Fund;

—a joint paper presenting the proposal for the fund;

—Annex 1 to the proposal entitled, The Zimbabwe Economy;
                                and

—Annex 2 to the proposal entitled, The Zimbabwe Development Fund:
                                Possible Program Areas.
